2. Pattern Matching
checking type and creating variable in one step.
Here:

check type
manually cast
Two steps.



Before:

if(obj instanceof String){
    String s = (String) obj;
}

Java 21:

if(obj instanceof String s){
    System.out.println(s);
}
Now:

type check
variable creation
casting

all in one line.

Simple meaning:

Type check + variable creation together.

Less code.

