. Sequenced Collections
Easier way to get first and last element.
If you worked with Lists/Sets and needed first/last element:
java// BEFORE — awkward old way
String first = list.get(0);
String last  = list.get(list.size() - 1);

// AFTER — Java 21 you used
String first = list.getFirst();
String last  = list.getLast();

// Reversed iteration you used
list.reversed().forEach(item -> process(item));

